{"tid":696430,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"法國 AXA 一般保險業務於香港市佔第一","createTime":"2018-06-10T06:03:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-10T07:53:19.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ee0b76d524982266d64d3f75ba02ad564087093a","tid":696430,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T06:03:18.000Z","msg":"支那保險係GI不敵 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但支那做LIFE好撚多, 真係多謝港豬<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180609/large/1528528729_4bbf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180609%2Flarge%2F1528528729_4bbf.jpg&h=96fe5dec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n根據保監局臨時統計數字，去年本港一般保險業務毛保費錄481.37億元，按年升5.8%。AXA安盛董事總經理（一般保險業務）胡奕銘指，去年公司錄7%增長，市佔率達10.3%，維持市場排名首位。不過，他預期一般保險市場今年仍具挑戰，相信增長會保持平穩。<br />\n<br />\n來自瑞士的胡奕銘上任半年，過去曾於泰國、新加坡等地工作。他直言，本港保險市場成熟，除了價格競爭激烈外，市面上的產品選擇亦眾多，尤其個人保障產品，如家居保、意外保險等，過去幾年的市場增長有限。<br />\n<br />\n他相信，今年一般保險市場的表現與去年分別不大，僱員醫保及颱風相關的賠償繼續對承保利潤帶來挑戰。不過，公司會著手提升產品保障及種類，並加強電子服務，包括計畫將一般保險索償申請全電子化。以家居保為例，客戶他日只需上存照片，已經可以完成索償申請，加快理賠速度。"},{"pid":"04963f9a1369e9a529e0d1f42f0db6abbfabce79","tid":696430,"uid":21052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T06:06:32.000Z","msg":"支那人好鐘意買life走資<br />\n想問下佢地會唔會係香港買返大陸保險公司既plan ？ 大陸係咪查到？"},{"pid":"cac872d67f5c0a33429089c7f5dce84a610ae67f","tid":696430,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"04963f9a1369e9a529e0d1f42f0db6abbfabce79","tid":696430,"uid":21052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T06:06:32.000Z","msg":"支那人好鐘意買life走資<br />\n想問下佢地會唔會係香港買返大陸保險公司既plan ？ 大陸係咪查到？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T06:08:57.000Z","msg":"封左碌銀聯卡走資, 依家難左"},{"pid":"dde9fdce06201bb327faa9429b4d8bbccb4f1629","tid":696430,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T06:10:01.000Z","msg":"究竟有多賤先會幫趁支那公司？<br />\n<br />\n友邦都唔夠支那人壽多, CLS <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n新造直接業務<br />\n個人人壽年度化保費：<br />\n<br />\n香港友邦 42億<br />\n支那人壽 45億<br />\n支銀人壽 37億<br />\n匯豐人壽 46億"},{"pid":"40da2a0d2f3e3f966e24850fc540684e475d724d","tid":696430,"uid":37874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cac872d67f5c0a33429089c7f5dce84a610ae67f","tid":696430,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"04963f9a1369e9a529e0d1f42f0db6abbfabce79","tid":696430,"uid":21052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T06:06:32.000Z","msg":"支那人好鐘意買life走資<br />\n想問下佢地會唔會係香港買返大陸保險公司既plan ？ 大陸係咪查到？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T06:08:57.000Z","msg":"封左碌銀聯卡走資, 依家難左"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T06:10:47.000Z","msg":"依舊係好多大陸人買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你唔封晒佢 佢地都會搵路落黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n遲d大陸知埋香港果邊財務 睇呢班人點算"},{"pid":"8362ee5c1fbe3672ae254fde1b1fa8e9457c1e79","tid":696430,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"40da2a0d2f3e3f966e24850fc540684e475d724d","tid":696430,"uid":37874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cac872d67f5c0a33429089c7f5dce84a610ae67f","tid":696430,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"04963f9a1369e9a529e0d1f42f0db6abbfabce79","tid":696430,"uid":21052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T06:06:32.000Z","msg":"支那人好鐘意買life走資<br />\n想問下佢地會唔會係香港買返大陸保險公司既plan ？ 大陸係咪查到？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T06:08:57.000Z","msg":"封左碌銀聯卡走資, 依家難左"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T06:10:47.000Z","msg":"依舊係好多大陸人買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你唔封晒佢 佢地都會搵路落黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 